tool_description: Convert HTML and CSS to PDFs with the help of the PrintCSS Cloud.
name: PrintCSS.cloud
title: PrintCSS.cloud

api_list.name: Render PDF
api_list.description:
This collection describes the REST endpoints of the PrintCSS Cloud (https://printcss.net/api).

You will need to subscribe to a plan on https://rapidapi.com/azettl/api/printcss-cloud/pricing to use this API.

All resources besides the HTML, CSS, and JavaScript need to be externally available via URL or sent as a base64 encoded ZIP file.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://printcss-cloud.p.rapidapi.com/render"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "printcss-cloud.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.post(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
